    ICONIX Property & Asset Management SB Job Vacancies 2021 - Tenant Management / Coordinator

    January 3, 2021

    TOC

    • Vacancy

    ICONIX Property & Asset Management SB job vacancies 2021 for Tenant Management / Coordinator position which based in Kota Damansara. Jawatan kosong ICONIX Property & Asset Management SB 2021 terkini untuk kekosongan Tenant Management / Coordinator penempatan di Kota Damansara.

    Vacancy

    • Tenant Management / Coordinator

    List-ID: 87901420Today 07:25
    Job Description
    The Tenant management person will be stationed at the site office and manage the site office and tenant communications. The person will also arrange and schedule any fixup needed for the property. Also to work with the building management office to submit and coordinate the fixup of the defects.
    • MALE preferred
    **Experience handling tenants/guests (HOTEL industry /Logistics) Preferred
    Location: KOTA DAMANSARA

    1. Handle tenant communication and able to properly explain & enforce the rules to tenants.
    2. Coordinate. schedule and follow up fixup & maintenance (plumber/contractors/electrician etc) to fixup any defects in property
    3. Ensure work done properly and communicated properly to the tenants

    We are looking for highly motivated, hardworking, good in speaking/communicating with people. Must be team player and good with coordinating work. Detailed and goal oriented. Have own transport and willing to travel between property locations.

    Able to start work Immediately
    Experience in any handling tenants/guests (Hotel industry/logistics) preferred

    Please Send CV
    Email: recruitment@iconixpropertymgmt.com
    Whatsapp ONLY: +6

    Show contact number

    , +60 16-560 4882
